The system abandons the asynchronous Actor Model in favor of a Synchronous ECS Data Pipeline. Instead of microservices communicating via database disk writes, the system loads all market data into memory as flat, columnar arrays (Components). A master "Tick Loop" passes this memory through sequential, stateless functions (Systems). This eliminates I/O bottlenecks, completely prevents race conditions, and guarantees deterministic execution.

