* **Module 3: The Portfolio Manager (XGBoost/Risk)**: Reads signals. Uses an XGBoost meta-model and Mean-Variance Optimization to calculate beta-weighted, volatility-targeted capital allocations. 
* **Module 4: The Execution Trader & CCO**: The ONLY module with broker API keys. Reads target portfolio, compares to actual broker state, checks Hard-To-Borrow fees, margin limits, and executes required delta trades based on liquidity heuristics.

## 3. Infrastructure & Hosting
* **Production Database**: Supabase (PostgreSQL). Acts as the single source of truth for all modules.
